From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Sun, 5 Oct 2025 14:22:06 -0700
Subject: perf dso: Clean up read_symbol() error handling
Git-commit: bca753204e9eab3bd56907ec5f5ed151094d7742
Patch-mainline: v6.18-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Ensure errno is set and return to caller for error handling.

Unusually for perf the value isn't negated as expected by
symbol__strerror_disassemble().

